Dear business team,

I would like to tell you about my disappointing experience in your café. In the past, I have regularly come to you on Sundays to buy bread and order cakes for special occasions. This always worked smoothly, which is why I decided to stop by for breakfast too.

Unfortunately I have to say that my last visit was even worse than expected. I sat at the table for over 10 minutes without being served, while other guests who arrived later were served immediately. There was even an incident where something was almost brought to me from the next table, but I was completely ignored there too.

Because of this experience, I decided to leave without ordering anything. It's unfortunate that I didn't feel valued as a long-time customer. I received a friendly farewell from the counter, but that didn't make up for the disappointing experience.

In the future, I will buy my bread elsewhere on Sundays and look for my cakes from a supplier who appreciates my appreciation. It's a shame that a negative experience has affected my relationship with your store, but I think there are other places that can better meet my needs.

Pleasant atmosphere. Very friendly staff. I like to train in Aadorf.
In particular, thank you very much for responding to the customer concern about opening hours. This means I can start the day sporty again from October :-)
(Although training in the evening also has its appeal (see photo))

I really enjoy training here. The staff is very friendly and conscientious. Great attention is paid to cleanliness (daily). Devices that are out of service are repaired very promptly.

For me it has all the training equipment I need. The only thing that would be cool is longer ropes for the cable pulleys so that you can hit the triceps better ;)

A very clean and well-equipped gym. The staff is very accommodating and a program was put together according to my wishes during the introduction. The Update Fitness in Aadorf is very modern and nice to look at. Even if there are a lot of people in the gym, you can still get your work done because it has so many machines. Personally, I have never tried the fitness programs in a separate room, but I have only received very good feedback there. Without a doubt one of the best fitness centers in the canton of Thurgau.

Compared to the update in Oberwil BL, the infrastructure is clean and not dingy. Likewise the devices. Free weight area rather small. Unfortunately only a Selizug tower. Overall, makes a good impression.

The employees in Aadorf are really very nice, but there are a lot of things I'm not happy with...
First of all, if something breaks, it will last FOREVER until it gets fixed. For example, the light in the women's toilet has been broken for about 2 months and we haven't repaired it. It's like blinking at the disco and when you're already exhausted from training, you almost collapse. Some devices can no longer be used for a very long time because they are never repaired.

Secondly, Update is constantly opening new gyms, but the existing ones are never expanded with, for example, new holds or more machines. Almost everyone only has the bare necessities, if at all.

And thirdly, it is extremely hot in summer. Every time I do it, I almost pass out or vomit because it's so warm! And I'm not the only one complaining about these things. But no, customers are not taken into account! Savings are being made wherever possible so that Update can make more money.
This can not be it! We pay for exactly these things! If it wasn't the only gym near me, I would have gone to another one long ago.
